# Shell 脚本强制 LF 行尾，否则 Windows 克隆出 CRLF 会让 bash 报 $'\r' 错误。
*.sh text eol=lf

# 规则、技能与脚本跨 Claude/Codex 同步，统一 LF，避免 Windows autocrlf 制造整文件 diff。
.gitattributes text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.R text eol=lf
*.svg text eol=lf

# Vendored upstream snapshots retain source bytes so recorded SHA-256 values stay portable.
skills/research-visuals/references/external/academic-figure-skill/** binary
skills/research-visuals/references/external/academic-figure-generator/** binary

# Windows hook 启动器固定 CRLF，避免不同 autocrlf 设置反复提示或改写。
*.cmd text eol=crlf
